---
title: Roast Chicken & Creamy Peppercorn Sauce with Easy ANZAC Biscuits for Dessert
description: One bite of this tender roast chicken, accompanied with elegant sides: crispy prosciutto greens, velvety mash and rosemary pangrattato makes it clear why the simple things are hard to beat. For the finale, whip up our no-fuss ANZAC biscuits with our special biscuit mix. All you need to do is a quick melt and stir!
